00:23:06,420 --> 00:23:07,240
Next time

494
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:10,590
A conclusion, that must follow a beginning.

495
00:23:10,590 --> 00:23:13,390
Our hope will be lead to a destruction?

496
00:23:13,390 --> 00:23:15,580
Our hope will be the very death?

497
00:23:15,580 --> 00:23:19,890
